    "bio_long": "Kevin is the Principal Investigator of CC Lab. He received his PhD from City University of Hong Kong (CityUHK) and completed postdoctoral training at The Ohio State University (OSU). Before joining XJTLU in 2024, he was at Zhejiang University (ZJU) developing machine learning algorithms for drug discovery. His research spans structural bioinformatics, molecular dynamics, and biological foundation models. He is also a member of the Center for Intelligent RNA Therapeutics at XJTLU.",
